properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 1 at 3:39AM EST until February 2 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds increasing to 20 kt this evening with
gusts near 30 kt and seas building 4 to 6 feet.

* WHERE...Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...From 4 PM this afternoon to 10 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 10 AM EST SUNDAY
